title: Louie Lopez in Los Angeles, CA
description:
Spend some time with Louie as he shares a little bit about what makes him tick. Shot in and around his hometown of Los Angeles, CA, watch Louie hit some pools, ditches, streets, bowls, and parks.

Video produced by Six Stair.
